The village is home to many renowned and powerful clans. Some known clans and notable members include:
Aburame, Shino;
Akimichi, Choji, Choza;
Hyūga, Hinata, Neji, Hanabi, Hizashi, Hiashi;
Inuzuka, Kiba;
Nara, Shikamaru;
Sarutobi, Asuma;
Senju, Tsunade;
Uchiha, Sasuke, Itachi;
Yamanaka, Ino, Inoichi;
